      public void solicitud_temperatura(Double multiplo, Double suma, String nombre)
      The function "solicitud_temperatura" takes in a multiple, a sum, and a name as parameters, prompts the user to enter a temperature, converts the temperature using the given multiple and sum, and displays the converted temperature with the given name.
      Parameters:
      multiplo - A double value representing the conversion factor from Celsius to Fahrenheit or Kelvin.
      suma - The parameter "suma" is used to calculate the sum of the temperature value and a constant value.
      nombre - The name of the temperature unit (e.g. "Celsius", "Fahrenheit", "Kelvin").

      public void solicitud_temperatura_s(Double resta, Double multiplo, Double suma, String nombre)
      This Java function prompts the user to enter a temperature, converts it using a given formula, and displays the converted temperature with the specified unit of measurement.
      Parameters:
      resta - A value used for subtraction in the temperature conversion formula.
      multiplo - The "multiplo" parameter is used to calculate the conversion factor for the temperature conversion. It represents the value by which the temperature should be multiplied to convert it to the desired unit.
      suma - The parameter "suma" is used to calculate the temperature conversion. It represents the value that needs to be added to the temperature in order to convert it to the desired unit.
      nombre - The parameter "nombre" is a String that represents the unit of measurement for the temperature.

      public void solicitud_temperatura_kf(Double resta, Double multiplo, Double suma, String nombre)
      This Java function prompts the user to enter a temperature, converts it using a formula, and displays the converted temperature with a specified unit of measurement.
      Parameters:
      resta - The value to subtract from the temperature before multiplying by the multiplo value and adding the suma value.
      multiplo - The "multiplo" parameter is used to calculate the conversion factor for converting the temperature from Kelvin to Fahrenheit.
      suma - The parameter "suma" is used to calculate the conversion from Kelvin to Fahrenheit. It represents the value that needs to be added to the result of the multiplication of the temperature by a certain factor.
      nombre - The name of the temperature unit (e.g., "Kelvin" or "Fahrenheit").
